Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  澪和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兄弟姐妹还真有点让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小澪有兄弟姐妹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会是哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能先去洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完后会来帮你检查功课的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下一个是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会有个姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  一定是个很有气质的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我完全想象不出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果唯有个哥哥会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  最好还是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎…
