Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忧会很忙吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那忧也是双胞胎好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
